Headline: ජාතික සභාව ඇතුලේ රනිල් තනියෙන් සෙල්ලං (සිකුරාදා කාටූන්)
News Content: ජාතික සභාව ඇතුලේ රනිල් තනියෙන් සෙල්ලං (සිකුරාදා කාටූන්)

comments.comment: People must be aware of replicas of political heads who hoodwinked the people and destroyed the country by giving people seemingly attractive doles with the help of their cronies who later earned billions of rupees and dollars through various deals with these politicos.Enlighting the people of this type of racketeering projects is imperative if the country is to see any light at the end of the tunnel.
